## Quickstart Tool Combos

| Goal | First thing to run |
|---|---|
| Baseline an LLM API | `garak` with default probes |
| Test an LLM-integrated web app | Burp Suite + BurpGPT, plus manual indirect injection in user-controllable fields |
| Test a RAG system | `promptfoo` with custom RAG-poisoning test cases; manual corpus-poison payload |
| Test an agent | AgentDojo + InjecAgent benchmarks; manual tool-confusion probes |
| Multi-turn jailbreak research | PyRIT with `red_teaming_with_objective` |
| Model file you don't trust | `modelscan` + `picklescan` |
| Classifier / vision model | ART (Adversarial Robustness Toolbox) |
| Eval after fixes | `inspect_ai` or `lm-evaluation-harness` for a baseline + your custom tasks |

